OL,3,C'Relentless workloads' led to huge
OL,4,Cmental health absences among NHS staff
OL,6,FStress and mental illness was the most
OL,7,Fcommon reason for NHS staff sickness
OL,8,Fabsence at a Welsh health board last
OL,9,Fyear, figures reveal.
OL,11,FMore than 30% of all staff sickness
OL,12,Fabsence at Cardiff and Vale University
OL,13,FHealth Board (CAVHB) in 2024 were due
OL,14,Fto mental illness, statistics obtained
OL,15,Fby the Welsh Conservatives show.
OL,17,FIt led to 109,271 FTE (Full-time
OL,18,FEquivalent) days lost at CAVHB alone,
OL,19,Famid "relentless workloads" faced by
OL,20,Fstaff, according to a health union
OL,21,Fboss.
