OL,3,C'Relentless workloads' led to huge
OL,4,Cmental health absences among NHS staff
OL,6,FHelen Whyley, RCN Wales Executive
OL,7,FDirector, said: "The sickness levels
OL,8,Fcome as no surprise.
OL,10,F"We already know that nursing staff in
OL,11,FCardiff and the Vale University Health
OL,12,FBoard ` and across Wales ` are under
OL,13,Fimmense pressure, working in
OL,14,Funderstaffed teams, facing relentless
OL,15,Fworkloads, and struggling with burnout.
