OL,3,C'Relentless workloads' led to huge
OL,4,Cmental health absences among NHS staff
OL,6,F"High sickness absence rates are a
OL,7,Fsymptom of a system that is failing to
OL,8,Fsupport its workforce. Nursing staff
OL,9,Fare being forced to provide care in
OL,10,Fhospital corridors due to bed
OL,11,Fshortages and staffing issues, a
OL,12,Fsituation that adds to their stress
OL,13,Fand exhaustion.
OL,15,F"Without urgent investment in safe
OL,16,Fstaffing levels and better working
OL,17,Fconditions, these pressures will
OL,18,Fcontinue to take a toll on the health
OL,19,Fand wellbeing of nursing staff,
OL,20,Fultimately impacting the care of
OL,21,Fpatients in Wales".
