OL,6,FIt comes as Wales' health secretary
OL,7,Fannounced escalated intervention
OL,8,Fmeasures at CAVHB amid concerns about
OL,9,Fa growing financial deficit.
OL,11,FJeremy Miles announced on March 11
OL,12,Fthat the health board will move to
OL,13,Flevel four for finance, strategy and
OL,14,Fplanning on the five-point scale, with
OL,15,Fspecial measures the highest at level
OL,16,Ffive.
