OL,6,FAcross Wales, Freedom of Information
OL,7,Ffigures show more than 19,000
OL,8,Foccurrences of sickness absence were
OL,9,Fcategorised under 'anxiety/stress/
OL,10,Fdepression/other psychiatric
OL,11,Fillnesses'.
OL,13,FWelsh Conservative Shadow Cabinet
OL,14,FSecretary for Health and Social Care,
OL,15,FJames Evans MS, called the absence
OL,16,Flevels "a symptom of the endemic
OL,17,Ffailure of Labour in Wales to manage
OL,18,Fthe Welsh NHS properly."
